: CELLS>TARGET
  0 DO OVER I CELLS + @ OVER I CELLS-T + !-T LOOP 2DROP ;

#THREADS T' FORTH-WORDLIST >BODY-T 03 + !-T
TLINKS T' FORTH-WORDLIST >BODY-T 06 + #THREADS CELLS>TARGET
THERE   T' DP             >BODY-T !-T

